OL,5, Labour has called for business rates to
OL,6, be scrapped to help firms struggling to
OL,7, cope with rising energy prices.        
OL,9,FThe party also urged the government to 
OL,10,Fintroduce a windfall tax on North Sea  
OL,11,Fgas and oil producers to create a #600m
OL,12,Ffund to support companies.             
OL,14,FBusinesses, like many households, have 
OL,15,Fseen their energy bills rise in recent 
OL,16,Fmonths along with wholesale gas prices.
OL,18,FThe government said it would listen to 
OL,19,Fpeople and businesses on how to manage 
OL,20,Fthe costs of energy.                   
